{"word":"Hebron","slug":"hebron","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Hebron</b> <a href=\"#/H2275\">H2275</a><br/><a href=\"#/H5683\">H5683</a> <br/> 1. A city of Asher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=28'>Jos 19:28</a><br/> 2. A city of Judah, south of Jerusalem:<br/> - When built<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=22'>Num 13:22</a> <br/> - Fortified<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=10'>2Ch 11:10</a> <br/> - Called Kirjath-Arba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=23&verse=2'>Gen 23:2</a> <br/> - Called Arba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=27'>Gen 35:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=13'>Jos 15:13</a> <br/> - Abraham dwells and Sarah dies at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=23&verse=2'>Gen 23:2</a> <br/> - Hoham, king of, confederated with other kings of the Canaanites against Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=39'>Jos 10:39</a> <br/> - Children of Anakim dwell at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=22'>Num 13:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=21'>Jos 11:21</a> <br/> - Conquest of, by Caleb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=14&verse=15'>Jos 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=10'>Jdg 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=20'>Jdg 1:20</a> <br/> - A city of refuge<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=20&verse=7'>Jos 20:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=11'>Jos 21:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=13'>Jos 21:13</a> <br/> - David crowned:<br/> b King of Judah at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=11'>2Sa 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3'>2Sa 3</a><br/> b King of Israel at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=5'>2Sa 5:5</a><br/> - The burial place of:<br/> b Sarah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=23&verse=2'>Gen 23:2</a><br/> b Abner<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=32'>2Sa 3:32</a><br/> b Ish-Bosheth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=12'>2Sa 4:12</a><br/> - The conspirators against Ish-Bosheth hanged at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=12'>2Sa 4:12</a> <br/> - Absalom made king at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=10'>2Sa 15:10</a> <br/> - Jews of the Babylonian captivity dwell at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=25'>Neh 11:25</a> <br/> - Pool of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=12'>2Sa 4:12</a> <br/> 3. Son of Kohath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=18'>Exo 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=19'>Num 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=2'>1Ch 6:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=18'>1Ch 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=12'>1Ch 23:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=19'>1Ch 23:19</a><br/> 4. The patronymic of Mareshah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=43'>1Ch 2:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=9'>1Ch 15:9</a>"}]}